
Todays Soft Skill Tip:

Day 15 – Presentation Flow: Guide, Don’t Overload

A good presentation isn’t about showing everything you know — it’s about guiding your audience through what matters most.

Think of it like storytelling: every slide or point should move your listener closer to understanding.

Your goal is not to impress — it’s to make others understand effortlessly.

Task:
Plan a 2-minute talk using this simple flow:
1️⃣ Why it matters
2️⃣ What you did or learned
3️⃣ How it created impact
